{"tid":2453010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔中年司機3日前險衝落海 今天台維修天線墮樓亡","createTime":"2021-03-19T07:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T17:43:19.000Z","uid":9347,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6cff1ef8fe59f3489e92e76057e43b3e24e850d7","tid":2453010,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"大埔一名56歲男子，3日前駕車在汀角路失事險衝落海，大命不死後，今早在洞梓村一村屋天台維修天線期間，懷疑失足墮樓死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方早上約11時接報，指一名男租客倒斃洞梓村一間村屋對開地上。據悉，事主任職汽車經紀，獨居村屋3樓，昨日曾向鄰居提及天線接收有問題，懷疑今早在天台維修天線時失足墮斃。<br />\n<br />\n而事主剛於3天前（周二，16日）在一宗車禍中大命不死。當日下午約1時37分，事主駕駛的白色私家沿汀角路駛經洞梓路一彎位時，疑失控衝落斜坡下的石灘，差一步便連人帶車墮海。事主事後報稱胸痛，送那打素醫院治理。私家車車頭損毀，由吊臂車拖走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cmsMDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cmsMDq.jpg&h=900f3e90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5887295a4783b79b088bbb6f38251e1fee9ed81","tid":2453010,"uid":9347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"Final destination 咁<br />\n算唔算係地獄黑仔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f88d4494a6bf5b1ea6c63537f780f05bf1e968","tid":2453010,"uid":19528,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"應該有買人壽保險"},{"pid":"ef879c79f266dff61e1cedc4021f7a134faeacbb","tid":2453010,"uid":3358,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12b5b2b76e05805cff6a7d2a58d72bc22fdf31f","tid":2453010,"uid":9347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef879c79f266dff61e1cedc4021f7a134faeacbb","tid":2453010,"uid":3358,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"個天有冇咁想佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a